            <thetext>qxWeb.attach does not allow overriding existing methods but this can be necessary when extending a module class. We should allow overriding, perhaps guarded by an additional parameter for attach so we can still warn in case of unintentional overriding.

Also, attach currently throws when trying to override in the debug version but silently overrides in the build version. The behavior should be the same in both versions.</thetext>
